Class ComponentsAbstractFactoryInterface

java.lang.Object
view.components.ComponentsAbstractFactoryInterface
Direct Known Subclasses:
ComponentsAbstractFactory
public abstract class ComponentsAbstractFactoryInterface extends Object
Interface que define a fábrica abstrata para a criação de componentes visuais.
